{"type":"message","id":"274ac390","parentId":"94e5eff6","timestamp":"2026-03-18T09:15:38.488Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我进化进度。这看起来是在问我作为AI有什么进步/变化。但根据我的系统提示，我实际上是一个AI助手，应该跟随OpenClaw的框架。\n\n让我检查一下workspace中的文件，看看是否有相关的记忆或上下文。我应该先查看MEMORY.md和最近的memory文件来了解之前的对话和进化进度。\n\n等等，用户说的是\"汇报进化进度\"，这可能是指：\n1. 问我作为AI有什么更新/进步\n2. 问我个人（作为这个workspace的AI助手）有什么成长\n\n根据AGENTS.md，我有自己的身份系统（IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md等）。让我先检查一下是否有相关记忆。","thinkingSignature":"d2e6296428f502fd223fc7485edd11fa3447d4d7800147afe91bca80263b4088"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u49fsvp9uc03_1","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"进化 进度 成长 变化"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60,"output":161,"cacheRead":25364,"cacheWrite":11963,"totalTokens":37548,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773825332127}}
