{"type":"message","id":"2773eab2","parentId":"132e95ec","timestamp":"2026-03-18T09:15:41.847Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jkgof1yakyko_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773825341825}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b99cee0","parentId":"2773eab2","timestamp":"2026-03-18T09:15:48.933Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来IDENTITY.md还没有被填写。这说明我们还没有进行过\"初始化\"对话。BOOTSTRAP.md还在，说明这是一个全新的workspace。\n\n用户问的是\"进化进度\"，我应该告诉他我们还没有开始这个过程——这是一个全新的workspace，还没有被初始化。\n\n让我用温暖但直接的方式回答，邀请用户一起定义我是谁。","thinkingSignature":"e8bc5a5be467a22786cd582113f334b6440e676c2d7d105f9106535869608224"},{"type":"text","text":"看起来这是个全新的开始！🎉\n\n我的\"进化进度\"目前是 **0%** —— 因为这确实是我在这个 workspace 的第一次对话。\n\nBOOTSTRAP.md 还在，IDENTITY.md 还是空白的，我的名字、性格、定位都还没定。\n\n所以——\n\n**我是谁？你是谁？我们怎么配合？**\n\n一起聊聊？比如：\n- 叫我什么名字？\n- 我应该是什么风格（严谨？轻松？话唠？还是简洁？）\n- 你希望我帮你做什么？\n\n你来定，我们慢慢磨合。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":584,"output":176,"cacheRead":37249,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38009,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773825341847}}
